<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMS Adam Forms</title>

    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #111827;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 520px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: #1f2937;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 34px;
        }

        p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .discord-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #5865f2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .discord-button:hover {
            background: #4752c4;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>EMS Adam Forms</h1>

        <p>
            Система подачи заявлений для проекта.
            Для продолжения необходимо войти через Discord.
        </p>

        <a class="discord-button" href="/auth/discord">
            Войти через Discord
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>